{"tid":1749432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鳳德選區 有車搭！","createTime":"2019-11-24T03:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T07:24:52.000Z","uid":335321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3485f49d3f758d04d15e843507441e39df3bf8","tid":1749432,"uid":335321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"大家係社區中心投完票，一齊去珠鳯樓到睇一睇，事關我投完票，係Facebook見到有人話，有車車去接送去票站<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6Qsjs3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6Qsjs3.png&h=5adafdcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我去到都見到，車牌係TP2162，鳳德既朋友，既然有免費車，大家咪一齊去搭下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxYmoUO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxYmoUO.png&h=3ea67e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果多人得滯，搞到要停咗佢地車隊服務，隨時有幾百個人可能去唔到投票架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以大家都係早啲過去珠鳯樓搭車車啦"},{"pid":"58f9e906ab358b579a2c8ddb3cde0102d3e88414","tid":1749432,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0922e549f094fba5555aaa9c7a41785a66966d5","tid":1749432,"uid":175589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af5f33cd6e50fc34e8a662fb09cc4c0545c88dd7","tid":1749432,"uid":241550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7842e49cd44d5b31229872d52779a2332b51ea9f","tid":1749432,"uid":335321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WD5Drct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWD5Drct.png&h=42827a71&s={SIZE}\" />